{"tid":975841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲豬瘟疫情失控  中国又出現新型伊波拉病毒  可傳人類","createTime":"2019-01-10T03:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T05:53:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e71eee96033273d868201e2db777cc4f01f27f","tid":975841,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:38:05.000Z","msg":"非洲豬瘟疫情在中國失控，但傳出有科學家在中國蝙蝠體內發現類伊波拉病毒，而且確定能感染包括人類在內的多種哺乳動物。<br />\n<br />\n根據馬來西亞媒體報導，新加坡「杜克-NUS醫學院」(Duke-NUS Medical School)傳染病研究主任王林發(譯音，Wang Lin-Fa)，以及中國科學院武漢分院的鄭正立以及研究團隊，在中國雲南捕獲的果蝠體內發現一種新型絲狀病毒，這個病毒可以感染猴子、狗與人類細胞，命名為「勐臘病毒（Měngl&agrave;）」。這種病毒與伊波拉病毒的演化有密切關係，因此王林發認為，研究這個病毒遺傳多樣性與地理分部十分重要，可事先進行風險評估與防疫等工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://globalnewstv.com.tw/201901/55390/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fglobalnewstv.com.tw%2F201901%2F55390%2F&d=XYjAR2kfDNRlBgPoxB6BaP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a184b2bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://globalnewstv.com.tw/201901/55390/</a>"},{"pid":"766ee3920daf0e9e490eb3d10f83f5968ae618e1","tid":975841,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42dc3cf8df94f0e349f6a8fb1879fcbba8bf73b4","tid":975841,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae42abbbfc674da02ba4fe40765927a85724b8d","tid":975841,"uid":886,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"唉，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b8a89e1064641e30c282f6ffbb97fa566e7af7","tid":975841,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c